  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<p>Prepare tender cost submission /pricing / quantity take off / costevaluation</p>\n<p>Obtaining quotations, liaising andnegotiate with sub-contractors andsuppliers</p>\n<p>Responsible for measuring quantitiesand taking off</p>\n<p>Prepare Variation Orders, claims andfinal accounts,</p>\n<p>Prepare sub contracts and sub-contractor payments</p>\n<p>All other QS related job</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirement:</p>\n<p>Degree / Diploma in Building or itsequivalent</p>\n<p>Able to work independently</p>\n<p>At least3 years of working experiencewith main contractor</p>\n<p>Computer literacy (MS Office).</p>",
